high_descs: Walk straight ahead to find the small white table with food and cutlery on it.
Pick up the metal ladle next to the bread
Turn right and walk straight. Turn right again and walk towards the sink.
Place the ladle in the sink, then turn on the faucet so water fills the sink. Turn off the faucet and retrieve the ladle.
Open the wooden cabinet below and to the right of the sink.
Place the ladle inside the cabinet and close th cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Find and clean the ladle before placing it in a cabinet near the sink.

high_descs: turn to the right, then turn left and head toward the table near the wall.
pick up the large spoon from behind the loaf of bread on the middle of the table.
turn left and head straight, then turn left until you reach the counter, then turn right and walk to the sink.
place the large spoon in the sink and turn on the water.
take the clean large spoon out of the sink
place the clean large spoon in the cabinet underneath the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean large spoon in the cabinet under the sink

high_descs: Turn to the right and take a step forward, then turn to the left and walk across the room, then turn to the left to face the table.
Take the spoon that is near the bread on the table.
Turn to the left and walk halfway across the room, then turn to the right and walk to the sink.
Put the spoon in the sink, then turn on the sink and let it fill, then take the spoon out of the sink once it has drained.
Look at the cupboards below the sink.
Open the cupboard on the right and place the spoon inside.
